without telling me?

30
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:45,350
- Come on.
- Sir.

31
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,550
[ Broadcasting Studio ]

32
00:01:45,420 --> 00:01:46,849
What are you doing? What?

33
00:01:46,850 --> 00:01:48,219
- What are you doing?
- Look.

34
00:01:48,220 --> 00:01:50,555
[ Hey! You'll be suspended for this! ]

35
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:54,485
[ Hey, Ho-rang! Hey! ]

36
00:01:54,790 --> 00:01:57,195
- Hold on.
[ - Ho-rang. ]

37
00:01:57,830 --> 00:01:59,425
[ - Ho-rang! ]
- I'll open it.

38
00:02:02,430 --> 00:02:04,265
[ Open the door. ]

39
00:02:11,580 --> 00:02:13,405
[ Hey, open it. ]

40
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,715
Hey, Ho-rang.

41
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:24,015
You're so annoying. Do you know that?

42
00:02:25,090 --> 00:02:28,225
- Jae-yi
- Why did you keep that to yourself?

43
00:02:28,430 --> 00:02:29,889
Hey, are you crying?

44
00:02:29,890 --> 00:02:31,629
What? No way. I'm not crying.

45
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,359
Okay. Let go of me.

46
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:34,799
Gosh. That was suffocating.

47
00:02:34,800 --> 00:02:36,329
Seriously. You're so cold.

48
00:02:36,330 --> 00:02:37,935
You act as if you're all tough.

49
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:40,569
Don't smile at me. It's more annoying.

50
00:02:40,570 --> 00:02:41,805
Ho-rang!

51
00:02:42,040 --> 00:02:43,235
You can say it there.

52
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,505
You should have told me.

53
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,579
Why are you guys crying?

54
00:02:48,580 --> 00:02:50,478
How could I not cry?

55
00:02:50,479 --> 00:02:52,179
I thought you were my best friend.

56
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:55,049
Hey. You don't have to be friends
for long to be best friends.

57
00:02:55,050 --> 00:02:56,689
What? I didn't know you were here.

58
00:02:56,690 --> 00:02:58,419
I was the first one here.

59
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,115
So what? She's my friend.

60
00:03:02,330 --> 00:03:03,425
I'm sorry.

61
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:08,325
Thanks to you guys,
I was able to tell the truth today.

62
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,369
- Ho-rang.
- Hey.

63
00:03:10,370 --> 00:03:11,599
That's okay.

64
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,735
Say it there.

65
00:03:14,070 --> 00:03:15,165
Oh, right.

66
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:19,209
By the way, where's Ji So-hyun?

67
00:03:19,210 --> 00:03:20,349
So-hyun?

68
00:03:20,350 --> 00:03:22,809
Oh, right. She went mental earlier.

69
00:03:22,810 --> 00:03:24,919
If you saw her crush Jeong Hui-su...

70
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,349
Who crushed whom?

71
00:03:26,350 --> 00:03:27,445
- What?
- What?

72
00:03:28,290 --> 00:03:31,085
Good going, guys. Seriously.

73
00:03:31,290 --> 00:03:34,089
The one who was supposed to have
a work-study day caused trouble.

74
00:03:34,090 --> 00:03:35,759
- Sir. That's...
- And one of you

75
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:38,225
made sure everyone heard about it.

76
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:41,899
And you. Are you a thug?

77
00:03:41,900 --> 00:03:43,199
Why would you hit people?

78
00:03:43,200 --> 00:03:45,769
Sir. She's totally crazy.

79
00:03:45,770 --> 00:03:47,669
You should have heard
what So-hyun said earlier.

80
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:50,209
- Goodness.
- And she hit me too. Right here.

81
00:03:50,210 --> 00:03:53,945
Look at this. My palm is all busted.
It's redder than yours.

82
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:57,179
- Why are you here?
- You told me to come, so I'm here.

83
00:03:57,180 --> 00:03:58,549
- I did?
- Yes.

84
00:03:58,550 --> 00:04:00,079
Since you're here, stand with them.

85
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:02,015
- What?
- You brats.

86
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:06,455
Were you in on it too?

87
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:09,785
- Yes.
- Then, stand right here.

88
00:04:10,130 --> 00:04:13,229
You know you guys are in huge trouble
for what you did today, right?

89
00:04:13,230 --> 00:04:14,469
Write an apology letter.

90
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:16,625
And you'll clean the auditorium
next week. Got it?

91
00:04:16,929 --> 00:04:18,435
Go away. You're giving me headaches.

92
00:04:18,739 --> 00:04:20,965
- And you, Ho-rang.
- Yes?

93
00:04:21,239 --> 00:04:23,635
I was informed that you're having
a work-study day until today.

94
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:25,835
Well, you can go home.

95
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:27,645
Do whatever you want.

96
00:04:28,610 --> 00:04:29,705
Gosh.

97
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:32,020
[ Teachers' Office ]

98
00:04:32,020 --> 00:04:34,749
That's so annoying. Why do we
have to clean the auditorium?

99
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:35,819
Because you had a fight.

100
00:04:35,820 --> 00:04:37,685
- You, be quiet.
- Gosh.

101
00:04:38,790 --> 00:04:40,019
- You do it.
- No, you do it all.

102
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:42,355
- Why me? You do it.
- You did it. Not me.

103
00:04:42,630 --> 00:04:44,999
Ho-rang, you're going back home, right?

104
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,095
What?

105
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:49,525
- Yes.
- I'll walk you home, then.

106
00:04:49,770 --> 00:04:51,399
That's okay. I'm not a kid.

107
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,795
Why not? We can take you home.

108
00:04:54,640 --> 00:04:56,035
I'm really okay.

109
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:57,575
And

110
00:05:00,510 --> 00:05:02,375
I need to talk to her too.

111
00:05:07,550 --> 00:05:09,115
You knew?

112
00:05:11,260 --> 00:05:12,355
What?

113
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,485
That I was going to do
the broadcast today.

114
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,155
Yes.

115
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,495
Eun-taek told me.

116
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:24,395
He was worried when you weren't in school.

117
00:05:25,840 --> 00:05:26,935
I know.

118
00:05:29,810 --> 00:05:30,905
You too.

119
00:05:32,610 --> 00:05:33,705
What?

120
00:05:33,809 --> 00:05:36,705
Jae-yi told me that
you were worried about me too.

121
00:05:39,650 --> 00:05:42,015
You were talking to Jeong Hui-su
during my broadcast.

122
00:05:43,350 --> 00:05:44,455
Yes.

123
00:05:46,360 --> 00:05:48,085
I told you not to get involved.

124
00:05:48,290 --> 00:05:49,985
You never listen to me.

125
00:05:57,440 --> 00:05:58,535
I'm sorry.

126
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:05,835
I thought I should apologize to you.

127
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:10,405
- And thank...
- I...

128
00:06:11,550 --> 00:06:13,415
- What?
- What?

129
00:06:14,290 --> 00:06:15,545
You can go first.

130
00:06:16,390 --> 00:06:17,555
Well,

131
00:06:20,220 --> 00:06:22,955
- When I saw your broadcast...
- Isn't that Baek Ho-rang?

132
00:06:23,490 --> 00:06:25,229
No way. She didn't go home yet.

133
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:26,599
- Right.
- It's like I saw a celebrity.

134
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,025
Exactly.

135
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:30,025
- Should we take a photo?
- A selfie?

136
00:06:30,300 --> 00:06:32,035
No, a photo of Baek Ho-rang.

137
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:40,535
The class will start soon.

138
00:06:40,650 --> 00:06:42,105
Let's talk later.

139
00:06:43,650 --> 00:06:45,875
Okay. Let's do that.

140
00:06:46,780 --> 00:06:48,345
- Bye.
- Okay.

141
00:06:48,820 --> 00:06:50,015
And

142
00:06:53,890 --> 00:06:56,085
I'll call you.

143
00:06:58,130 --> 00:06:59,225
Okay.

144
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:01,065
Have a good day.

145
00:07:02,570 --> 00:07:03,495
Okay.

146
00:07:19,050 --> 00:07:19,949
That's her.

147
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:22,319
So she's the one who acted like the victim
to do that?

148
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:24,389
- She's a lunatic.
- What's wrong with her?

149
00:07:24,390 --> 00:07:28,325
- That's Jeong Hui-su.
- She's so thick-skinned.

150
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,485
Don't tell the others.

151
00:07:31,360 --> 00:07:32,625
It's a misunderstanding.

152
00:07:33,300 --> 00:07:37,365
What I told you that day wasn't a lie.

153
00:07:37,370 --> 00:07:38,239
Baek Ho-rang...

154
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,235
I'll leave the door unlocked,

155
00:07:40,910 --> 00:07:43,605
so pack your things and leave the
broadcasting team when nobody is there.

156
00:07:47,210 --> 00:07:50,145
- Hey, Ko Eun-taek. Hear the full story...
- That's enough.

157
00:07:53,350 --> 00:07:54,845
I think that Ko Eun-taek

158
00:07:55,720 --> 00:07:58,255
is being really considerate to you.

159
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:14,369
What about Baek Ho-rang? Did she go home?

160
00:08:14,370 --> 00:08:16,539
Yes. I contacted her earlier,
and that's what she said.

161
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:20,635
I feel relieved now. Before,
I felt like something was gnawing at me.

162
00:08:20,750 --> 00:08:22,779
Hey, Kim Yu-shin. Take a look at this.

163
00:08:22,780 --> 00:08:25,375
- What is it?
- Which one is prettier?

164
00:08:26,420 --> 00:08:27,749
- This one.
- Okay.

165
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:30,659
If I choose the opposite of you,
Do Woo-jae will like it.

166
00:08:30,660 --> 00:08:32,015
What's with the watches suddenly?

167
00:08:32,420 --> 00:08:35,489
Honestly, it's my 1,000th-day anniversary
with Do Woo-jae soon.

168
00:08:35,490 --> 00:08:36,828
Oh, is that so?

169
00:08:36,829 --> 00:08:39,799
So we promised to get each other gifts
and surprise each other.

170
00:08:39,800 --> 00:08:40,965
It's a secret.

171
00:08:41,329 --> 00:08:43,229
You promised to surprise each other?

172
00:08:43,230 --> 00:08:45,369
- What? Is that even possible?
- Yes.

173
00:08:45,370 --> 00:08:48,909
We'll prepare our gifts separately
and show them to each other on that day.

174
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:51,435
It'll be exciting.
Just like when we first started dating.

175
00:08:52,440 --> 00:08:54,309
You guys are really incredible.

176
00:08:54,310 --> 00:08:56,709
- How so?
- That means you fought for 1,000 days.

177
00:08:56,710 --> 00:08:59,445
Hey. It's not like we fight every day.

178
00:09:01,020 --> 00:09:02,645
We don't fight anymore.

179
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,589
We won't fight anymore.

180
00:09:06,590 --> 00:09:07,889
We don't fight.

181
00:09:07,890 --> 00:09:08,889
- Oh, my.
- What's that?

182
00:09:08,890 --> 00:09:12,029
You should've taken your time.
I told you I'd wait out front.

183
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:13,355
I saw you.

184
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,939
Are you going to eat with us?

185
00:09:17,940 --> 00:09:19,769
No. I'm going to go home.

186
00:09:19,770 --> 00:09:21,509
Come to think of it, why are you here?

187
00:09:21,510 --> 00:09:23,039
Is Ji So-hyun at the broadcasting studio?

188
00:09:23,040 --> 00:09:25,439
Yes. She must be busy because of
the video festival.

189
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:28,275
My dear So-hyun will get sick
if she works too hard.

190
00:09:29,050 --> 00:09:30,049
That's right.

191
00:09:30,050 --> 00:09:32,749
Come to think of it,
who prepared the broadcast today?

192
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:36,085
I doubt that the meticulous Ko Eun-taek
would've let it slide.

193
00:09:36,090 --> 00:09:37,859
I heard Ko Eun-taek prepared it.

194
00:09:37,860 --> 00:09:39,989
He did? It was Ko Eun-taek?

195
00:09:39,990 --> 00:09:43,385
Eun-taek. I didn't see him like that,
but he's so loving.

196
00:09:43,490 --> 00:09:44,655
You're right.

197
00:09:44,930 --> 00:09:47,965
But he's not as loving as Do Woo-jae.

198
00:09:50,230 --> 00:09:52,699
Do Woo-jae. I don't need anything big.

199
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:53,765
You know that, right?

200
00:09:55,840 --> 00:09:56,865
Yes.

201
00:10:04,620 --> 00:10:05,949
[ Baek Ho-rang, 72,000 followers ]

202
00:10:05,950 --> 00:10:12,960
[ View all 2,504 comments. ]

203
00:10:07,890 --> 00:10:09,689
[ Ho-rang, I heard you were a victim. ]

204
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,659
[ - You seem so pitiful now.
- I talked badly about you. ]

205
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,459
[ - I feel bad now.
- People are so quick to judge. ]

206
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:15,185
[ - I saw your broadcast. Be strong.
- Be strong. ]

207
00:10:17,800 --> 00:10:19,395
[ To tell you the truth, ]

208
00:10:20,030 --> 00:10:21,699
I'm a victim of school bullying.

209
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:22,965
[ Isn't that Baek Ho-rang? ]

210
00:10:23,030 --> 00:10:24,699
No way. She didn't go home yet.

211
00:10:24,700 --> 00:10:26,169
[ It's like I saw a celebrity. ]

212
00:10:26,170 --> 00:10:27,335
[ Exactly. ]

213
00:10:36,350 --> 00:10:38,115
[ Captain of the Broadcasting Team,
Ko Eun-taek ]

214
00:10:47,490 --> 00:10:50,255
[ Captain of the Broadcasting Team,
Ko Eun-taek ]

215
00:10:57,540 --> 00:10:58,535
What do you think?

216
00:10:58,770 --> 00:11:01,939
What's this?
Did you video call me to show me that?

217
00:11:01,940 --> 00:11:05,635
[ Yes. I figured you didn't get to see it
because you went straight home. ]

218
00:11:05,980 --> 00:11:07,205
[ Isn't it pretty? ]

219
00:11:07,850 --> 00:11:10,209
[ You're right. It's pretty. ]

220
00:11:10,210 --> 00:11:12,545
I didn't call to show you that.

221
00:11:12,850 --> 00:11:14,045
I wanted to see your face...

222
00:11:14,620 --> 00:11:16,815
What's this? Didn't you go home?

223
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,885
I'm at home.

224
00:11:19,220 --> 00:11:20,925
You dress like that at home?

225
00:11:21,030 --> 00:11:22,129
[ Did you go out somewhere? ]

226
00:11:22,130 --> 00:11:24,625
What are you talking about?
I dress like this normally.

227
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,595
[ This is a completely natural look. ]

228
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:29,925
- Natural?
- What?

229
00:11:33,340 --> 00:11:35,339
- Are you going home now?
[ - Yes. ]

230
00:11:35,340 --> 00:11:38,075
There were some things to take care of
for the video festival.

231
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:41,045
No wonder you didn't call.

232
00:11:41,310 --> 00:11:43,579
Oh, were you waiting for my call?

233
00:11:43,580 --> 00:11:46,319
What? I was waiting for you to call,

234
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:49,115
but I wasn't only thinking about
whether you would call.

235
00:11:51,790 --> 00:11:53,959
- Don't smile.
[ - I'm not smiling. ]

236
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,329
I always look like I'm smiling.

237
00:11:55,330 --> 00:11:58,429
Please. You never look like you're
smiling. You look like you're frowning.

238
00:11:58,430 --> 00:11:59,595
Hey, you.

239
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:08,165
So how did you feel today?

240
00:12:09,370 --> 00:12:11,305
[ You made a big decision
to say something. ]

241
00:12:12,310 --> 00:12:14,105
That's why it would've been harder.

242
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:17,845
If I'm being honest with you,

243
00:12:18,980 --> 00:12:20,575
I am worried.

244
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:23,185
[ More than feeling relieved, ]

245
00:12:23,250 --> 00:12:25,585
it's true that I feel more worried.

246
00:12:26,760 --> 00:12:27,985
But

247
00:12:28,830 --> 00:12:30,285
I don't feel bad.

248
00:12:31,130 --> 00:12:32,295
I feel relieved.

249
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:34,925
That's good.

250
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,465
Ko Eun-taek.

251
00:12:39,500 --> 00:12:40,565
What?

252
00:12:42,670 --> 00:12:44,405
Do you want to hang out tomorrow?

253
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:19,080
[ Ho-rang, I'm sorry. ]

254
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:23,180
[ Baek Ho, Kim Yu, Kang Jae ]

255
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:20,579
[ I wanted to hang out with you today, ]

256
00:13:20,580 --> 00:13:22,679
[ but I promised to volunteer
at the library with So-hyun. ]

257
00:13:22,680 --> 00:13:24,780
