266
00:13:51,280 --> 00:13:53,105
Gosh, it's cold.

267
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:09,655
Why are you taking it out?
You look cute with it.

268
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:11,195
What?

269
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,095
It's a bit smeared here.

270
00:14:27,310 --> 00:14:28,705
Your hair...

271
00:14:31,080 --> 00:14:32,875
Does it look awkward?

272
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:43,285
Does it look bad?

273
00:14:49,530 --> 00:14:50,495
No.

274
00:14:51,100 --> 00:14:53,295
Hey, I'm hungry. Let's go.

275
00:14:55,940 --> 00:14:56,965
Wait for me.

276
00:14:57,370 --> 00:14:59,480
