277
00:14:58,110 --> 00:15:00,179
You can wait right here.

278
00:15:00,180 --> 00:15:02,109
- Okay.
- So-hyun. I'm so excited.

279
00:15:02,110 --> 00:15:03,749
How many volunteer hours do you have left?

280
00:15:03,750 --> 00:15:05,875
After this, I have 10 hours left.

281
00:15:06,420 --> 00:15:09,019
Then you just need to come to the library
two more times with me. Right?

282
00:15:09,020 --> 00:15:10,419
How many hours do you have left?

283
00:15:10,420 --> 00:15:11,489
I filled them already.

284
00:15:11,490 --> 00:15:13,059
- You filled them already?
- Yes.

285
00:15:13,060 --> 00:15:14,859
My dream last year was to become
Mother Theresa.

286
00:15:14,860 --> 00:15:16,825
So I would leave school early
to go volunteer.

287
00:15:17,630 --> 00:15:18,959
Then why did you come today?

288
00:15:18,960 --> 00:15:21,865
Isn't it obvious?
I wanted to spend time with you.

289
00:15:21,930 --> 00:15:24,535
I even pushed my plans with Ho-rang
for this.

290
00:15:24,840 --> 00:15:26,199
How is she?

291
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,769
Who? Ho-rang?

292
00:15:27,770 --> 00:15:29,609
- Ji So-hyun?
- Oh, my.

293
00:15:29,610 --> 00:15:31,509
It is you, Ji So-hyun.

294
00:15:31,510 --> 00:15:33,039
It's been so long.

295
00:15:33,040 --> 00:15:34,609
I know. Have you been well?

296
00:15:34,610 --> 00:15:36,045
Yes. Have you been well?

297
00:15:36,510 --> 00:15:38,179
We went to the same middle school.

298
00:15:38,180 --> 00:15:40,019
I see. Hi. I'm Kim Yu-shin.

299
00:15:40,020 --> 00:15:41,075
Hi.

300
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:43,189
Can all the volunteers come over here?

301
00:15:43,190 --> 00:15:44,319
- Okay.
- Okay.

302
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,285
- It's been so long.
- I know.

303
00:15:48,160 --> 00:15:49,785
How did you find out about this place?

304
00:15:54,730 --> 00:15:57,099
- You like sushi from this place.
- I do?

305
00:15:57,100 --> 00:15:59,835
Didn't you leave the library last time
to eat this?

306
00:15:59,970 --> 00:16:00,895
No.

307
00:16:01,240 --> 00:16:03,365
I left to have dinner with you.

308
00:16:03,810 --> 00:16:07,075
- What?
- Kim Yu-shin said you always ate alone,

309
00:16:07,210 --> 00:16:08,505
so I wanted to eat with you.

310
00:16:11,420 --> 00:16:12,545
Hey, Ko Eun-taek.

311
00:16:13,950 --> 00:16:16,945
Are you more comfortable with
phone calls or texting?

312
00:16:17,990 --> 00:16:20,555
Phone calls.
I feel like texts are too cold.

313
00:16:20,820 --> 00:16:22,925
That's exactly what Kim Yu-shin said.

314
00:16:22,990 --> 00:16:24,529
Do you talk on the phone with him often?

315
00:16:24,530 --> 00:16:25,425
I guess so.

316
00:16:26,300 --> 00:16:28,225
He once called me 12 times in one day.

317
00:16:29,230 --> 00:16:30,765
Kim Yu-shin is such a nuisance.

318
00:16:31,370 --> 00:16:33,465
People don't call over 10 times a day
when they're dating.

319
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,005
Why?

320
00:16:35,310 --> 00:16:38,505
I guess you've called your girlfriends
at least 10 times a day.

321
00:16:38,940 --> 00:16:40,905
- What?
- So tell me.

322
00:16:41,310 --> 00:16:44,375
For how long have you dated someone?

323
00:16:45,220 --> 00:16:46,245
Why do you ask?

324
00:16:46,450 --> 00:16:48,745
I'm just a bit curious.

325
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:52,259
200 days.

326
00:16:52,260 --> 00:16:55,129
Gosh, you didn't hesitate,
and you told me right away.

327
00:16:55,130 --> 00:16:56,629
That's because you asked me.

328
00:16:56,630 --> 00:16:58,655
You have such a good memory.

329
00:16:58,860 --> 00:16:59,855
No.

330
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:01,929
Maybe you're just tactless.

331
00:17:01,930 --> 00:17:03,199
Hey! You were the one who first...

332
00:17:03,200 --> 00:17:05,995
It must've been so easy for you
since everything fits.

333
00:17:07,870 --> 00:17:11,405
Ho-rang, are you being jealous right now?

334
00:17:12,810 --> 00:17:14,745
What are you talking about? Just eat.

335
00:17:15,910 --> 00:17:18,079
No, you're definitely mad.

336
00:17:18,080 --> 00:17:20,218
What are you talking about? I'm fine.

337
00:17:20,219 --> 00:17:22,285
We have a long day today.

338
00:17:22,890 --> 00:17:25,619
You have a minute and 20 seconds
to finish this.

339
00:17:25,620 --> 00:17:27,559
The food came out eight minutes ago.

340
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:28,655
Whatever.

341
00:17:36,370 --> 00:17:38,965
It's narrow. Get out of the way.

342
00:17:39,540 --> 00:17:42,165
Why don't you get out of the way?
I don't have any space to move.

343
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,555
- Hey!
- Hey!

344
00:18:01,330 --> 00:18:03,325
Don't fall asleep today.
Try to watch until the end.

345
00:18:03,560 --> 00:18:04,855
I won't!

346
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:08,429
Did you only buy one hand warmer,
by the way?

347
00:18:08,430 --> 00:18:10,725
Yes, that was the last one.

348
00:18:19,910 --> 00:18:21,575
Your hands look cold.

349
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:49,009
So-hyun, isn't it so much work?
Do you want me to do it instead?

350
00:18:49,010 --> 00:18:51,235
It's fine. I'm done with everything
except for these.

351
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:53,609
You like this book too?

352
00:18:53,610 --> 00:18:54,709
You know this book?

353
00:18:54,710 --> 00:18:56,105
Of course I do.

354
00:18:59,250 --> 00:19:01,415
This is by the same author.
Have you read it before?

355
00:19:01,450 --> 00:19:03,949
Yes, I've read everything
except for the most recent one.

356
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:05,659
I have the most recent one at home.

357
00:19:05,660 --> 00:19:06,815
Do you want to borrow it?

358
00:19:08,530 --> 00:19:09,625
Why?

359
00:19:09,730 --> 00:19:12,855
It's just a surprise.

360
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:15,365
You don't seem like the bookworm type.

361
00:19:17,130 --> 00:19:19,935
So-hyun, you're so good at being blunt
with that smile of yours.

362
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:22,109
My mom never made me study,

363
00:19:22,110 --> 00:19:24,135
but she always made me read books
since I was a child.

364
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:28,305
Is it charming to you?

365
00:19:28,710 --> 00:19:30,005
Did I get some points?

366
00:20:12,620 --> 00:20:13,815
Do you need help with these?

367
00:20:14,260 --> 00:20:15,355
Yes.

368
00:20:15,930 --> 00:20:17,189
- So-hyun!
- Hey!

369
00:20:17,190 --> 00:20:18,899
It's been so long.

370
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:21,569
Yes, it's been about three years.

371
00:20:21,570 --> 00:20:23,369
Yes, three years.

372
00:20:23,370 --> 00:20:25,765
We volunteered at the library together
back then too.

373
00:20:25,870 --> 00:20:27,165
Good times.

374
00:20:27,370 --> 00:20:29,769
We did? I don't remember.

375
00:20:29,770 --> 00:20:32,309
What? You can't remember?

376
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:34,875
You don't remember volunteering
at the school library together?

377
00:20:35,110 --> 00:20:38,715
I'm sorry, I don't remember.

378
00:20:41,180 --> 00:20:44,485
Do you remember dating me?

379
00:20:46,760 --> 00:20:48,289
We dated?

380
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:50,759
What? That's heartbreaking.

381
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:52,095
How can you forget that?

382
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,659
We dated for a whole month.

383
00:20:53,660 --> 00:20:55,325
We did?

384
00:20:55,830 --> 00:20:58,395
You right there, can you come here
for a moment?

385
00:20:58,500 --> 00:20:59,665
Hold on.

386
00:21:01,470 --> 00:21:03,839
So-hyun, this is Kilgour's book, right?

387
00:21:03,840 --> 00:21:05,579
- I'll take care of it.
- No, I will.

388
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:06,775
It's fine.

389
00:21:15,490 --> 00:21:16,849
What would you like to order?

390
00:21:16,850 --> 00:21:19,755
I'll take a toasted meatball sandwich.

391
00:21:20,260 --> 00:21:21,359
What about you?

392
00:21:21,360 --> 00:21:23,525
I'll take the steak and cheese one.

393
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:28,995
Be honest with me.

394
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:30,825
You cried earlier, right?

395
00:21:31,570 --> 00:21:33,965
I heard you sniffle at the end.

396
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:36,135
What are you talking about? No.

397
00:21:36,710 --> 00:21:37,965
You definitely cried.

398
00:21:38,440 --> 00:21:40,209
I saw you blow your nose on your sleeve.

399
00:21:40,210 --> 00:21:43,175
I didn't blow on my sleeve,
I blew on a tissue!

400
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:45,645
Goodness.

401
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:49,415
You're the one who was touched by a movie
that you know all the lines to.

402
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:53,515
That's because it's my first time watching
to the end with you.

403
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:57,425
Why does your talk get smoother every day?

404
00:22:00,460 --> 00:22:02,299
What's next?

405
00:22:02,300 --> 00:22:03,925
It's your turn now.

406
00:22:04,430 --> 00:22:05,595
Next,

407
00:22:06,900 --> 00:22:09,105
we're going to a place that I've always
wanted to take you.

408
00:22:09,210 --> 00:22:12,009
5, 4, 3,

409
00:22:12,010 --> 00:22:13,705
2, 1.

410
00:22:15,180 --> 00:22:16,879
[ Don't move when the photo is
being taken! ]

411
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:19,245
What was that? I thought you were
great at taking photos.

412
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,175
I look great.

413
00:22:21,450 --> 00:22:22,885
You look so awkward.

414
00:22:23,020 --> 00:22:25,685
I've never taken any
without sponsored products.

415
00:22:27,060 --> 00:22:29,189
Let's take one more. I'll take this one.

416
00:22:29,190 --> 00:22:30,429
Another one?

417
00:22:30,430 --> 00:22:33,259
It's like you're taking mock exams.

418
00:22:33,260 --> 00:22:35,465
Might as well take the best shots
while we're here.

419
00:22:37,170 --> 00:22:39,195
You deleted all of your photos
on your social media.

420
00:22:48,710 --> 00:22:49,909
[ Tigrrrrrre ]

421
00:22:49,910 --> 00:22:51,149
[ Posts ]

422
00:22:51,150 --> 00:22:52,449
[ Delete ]

423
00:22:52,450 --> 00:22:54,249
[ Delete Post? ]

424
00:22:54,250 --> 00:22:55,185
[ Deleting ]

425
00:22:55,190 --> 00:22:56,149
[ Tigrrrrrre ]

426
00:22:56,150 --> 00:22:57,289
[ Delete Post? ]

427
00:22:57,290 --> 00:22:58,655
[ Deleting ]

428
00:23:04,030 --> 00:23:05,125
[ So, ]

429
00:23:05,260 --> 00:23:08,595
since you don't take photos for likes
anymore, take more with me.

430
00:23:12,570 --> 00:23:14,495
Do it better this time.

431
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:18,939
5, 4, 3,

432
00:23:18,940 --> 00:23:20,775
2, 1.

433
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:35,655
This one looks good.

434
00:23:35,790 --> 00:23:37,385
It's not bad.

435
00:23:39,630 --> 00:23:41,965
Where did I leave my phone?

436
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:44,465
- Do you want me to call it?
- Yes, please.

437
00:23:56,080 --> 00:23:58,545
I left it inside? That's good.

438
00:24:02,420 --> 00:24:03,585
What's wrong?

439
00:24:03,820 --> 00:24:05,559
"Ko Eun-taek, SHBS Captain"?

440
00:24:05,560 --> 00:24:07,115
Isn't that too cold?

441
00:24:08,230 --> 00:24:11,025
It's easier to recognize you that way.

442
00:24:12,000 --> 00:24:14,159
You can't recognize it if it just says
my name?

443
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:17,165
And do you save everyone else
like this too?

444
00:24:17,630 --> 00:24:19,339
Yes, I'm telling you.

445
00:24:19,340 --> 00:24:20,435
Show me.

446
00:24:20,700 --> 00:24:21,965
I'll show you.

447
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:25,110
Look here.

448
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:27,175
[ Yu-shin ]

449
00:24:28,680 --> 00:24:29,845
How come he has a heart?

450
00:24:31,180 --> 00:24:32,250
What heart?

451
00:24:32,250 --> 00:24:33,345
[ Yu-shin ]

452
00:24:33,780 --> 00:24:35,549
What? What's this?

453
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,145
I had no idea!

454
00:24:37,420 --> 00:24:38,515
Whatever.

455
00:24:38,520 --> 00:24:40,955
I really didn't know!

456
00:24:41,290 --> 00:24:42,585
Let's change it.

457
00:24:42,690 --> 00:24:44,955
Watch. Kim Yu-shin.

458
00:24:45,300 --> 00:24:46,395
All good now?

459
00:24:46,700 --> 00:24:49,595
- Whatever.
- Don't get mad.

460
00:24:50,830 --> 00:24:52,835
- Don't your arms hurt?
- No.

461
00:24:54,370 --> 00:24:56,410
[ A heart beside your name?
You want to die? ]

462
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:57,940
[ Baek Ho-rang ]

463
00:24:56,470 --> 00:24:58,265
[ When did you do that on my phone? ]

464
00:24:58,540 --> 00:24:59,735
[ I love you too! ]

465
00:25:01,310 --> 00:25:02,845
[ Your Face account is still the same. ]

466
00:25:02,910 --> 00:25:04,645
[ Do you mind if I message you more often? ]

467
00:25:10,690 --> 00:25:12,155
- Yu-shin,
- Yes?

468
00:25:13,160 --> 00:25:14,515
why do you...

469
00:25:16,930 --> 00:25:18,025
Never mind.

470
00:25:18,430 --> 00:25:20,499
Time went by so fast today,
all thanks to you.

471
00:25:20,500 --> 00:25:21,769
- Really?
- Yes.

472
00:25:21,770 --> 00:25:24,029
Then promise me to invite me
the next time you go volunteering.

473
00:25:24,030 --> 00:25:25,495
- Okay?
- All right.

474
00:25:26,340 --> 00:25:28,909
It's so cold now that the sun is down.

475
00:25:28,910 --> 00:25:31,569
You're cold? Take my jacket.

476
00:25:31,570 --> 00:25:33,379
No, it's the middle of winter. It's fine.

477
00:25:33,380 --> 00:25:35,509
- You wear it.
- No, I'm not cold at all.

478
00:25:35,510 --> 00:25:36,605
Put it on.

479
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:42,715
- Thanks.
- It's nothing.

480
00:25:46,120 --> 00:25:48,585
Yu-shin, today...

481
00:25:51,260 --> 00:25:53,429
You're cold, aren't you?
Let me give this back.

482
00:25:53,430 --> 00:25:56,329
No, I told you that I'm a warm person.

483
00:25:56,330 --> 00:25:58,735
Keep talking. What were you saying?

484
00:25:59,270 --> 00:26:00,365
Well,

485
00:26:01,170 --> 00:26:03,109
do you know what Ho-rang is doing today?

486
00:26:03,110 --> 00:26:05,105
She's meeting someone today.

487
00:26:06,680 --> 00:26:10,809
So-hyun, I'm not trying to play tricks
or anything,

488
00:26:10,810 --> 00:26:14,275
- Yes?
- but can I put my hand in the pocket?

489
00:26:14,380 --> 00:26:15,919
Of course you can.

490
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,215
Thank you.

491
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:22,985
Ho-rang said that she was heading out
to meet someone today.

492
00:26:23,160 --> 00:26:26,025
I thought Jae-yi and I were
the only friends that she has.

493
00:26:26,030 --> 00:26:27,155
It's a relief.

494
00:26:28,830 --> 00:26:30,599
But remember how she said on the radio

495
00:26:30,600 --> 00:26:32,469
that she couldn't tell her only friend?

496
00:26:32,470 --> 00:26:35,239
I thought that'd be me,
but it turns out, it wasn't.

497
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:36,335
Who could that be?

498
00:26:44,380 --> 00:26:46,315
It's beautiful here.

499
00:26:49,720 --> 00:26:51,115
I thought you'd enjoy it.

500
00:26:52,160 --> 00:26:53,919
How did you find this spot?

501
00:26:53,920 --> 00:26:55,855
I stayed up all night
trying to find a place

502
00:26:57,560 --> 00:26:59,895
that you might like.

503
00:27:01,260 --> 00:27:02,665
This is fascinating.

504
00:27:04,470 --> 00:27:05,565
What do you mean?

505
00:27:07,800 --> 00:27:09,709
When we first met,

506
00:27:09,710 --> 00:27:12,335
I had no idea that we'd be here together.

507
00:27:17,310 --> 00:27:19,815
When we first met, you were...

508
00:27:21,220 --> 00:27:22,315
Goodness.

509
00:27:23,220 --> 00:27:24,445
Likewise.

510
00:27:24,620 --> 00:27:27,155
I didn't like you
when we first met either.

511
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:32,655
Seriously. I didn't even imagine that
I would enjoy having a meal with you

512
00:27:33,130 --> 00:27:35,925
and stand here,
watching the view with you.

513
00:27:36,830 --> 00:27:38,995
Never in a million years.

514
00:27:42,140 --> 00:27:43,335
And

515
00:27:48,010 --> 00:27:52,275
I really didn't think
I would end up liking you this much.

516
00:27:58,620 --> 00:28:00,615
I like you, Eun-taek.

517
00:28:04,060 --> 00:28:06,555
I should have told you this sooner.

518
00:28:08,230 --> 00:28:10,465
But I just couldn't find
the right time to tell you.

519
00:28:23,050 --> 00:28:24,745
